Name: Duchess Candace Liao
Details:
Born 2988.

The eldest child of the current Chancellor of the Capellan Confederation, the Duchess of St. Ives is the heir apparent to the throne after Maximillan had a falling out with his only son, Tormana. Candace was a skilled MechWarrior with the St. Ives Lancers with a combat injury suffered in 3017 forced her to retire from combat.
